data.revised_prompt: Create a captivating image of the Seattle skyline incorporating the expressive and symbolic use of line, color, and form that are characteristic of the post-impressionist era, akin to the artistic style of Van Gogh, who mainly worked with oil paints. Emphasize swirling skies, reflective waters and vibrant hues to capture the essence of this bustling metropolitan landscape.
